{"data":[{"date":"10:54 06/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p: \"Pogba l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/Lionel-Messi-muon-Barca-mua-Paul-Pogba-cua-MU-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Uruguay cho m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lloris ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\r\n</h2><h2>Pogba l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t Kante, Paul Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 ch\u00ednh trong c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, vai tr\u00f2, t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Pogba c\u0169ng quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n theo n\u0103m th\u00e1ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Hugo Lloris \u0111\u00e3 ca ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Uruguay:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, Pogba \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i Man United, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Juventus, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111ang ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, b\u1edfi Pogba l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c, m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o thi\u00ean b\u1ea9m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hugo Lloris ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh\" title=\"Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Lionel-Messi-muon-Barca-mua-Paul-Pogba-cua-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hugo Lloris ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y tham v\u1ecdng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi \u0111\u1ea5u xung quanh m\u00ecnh. World Cup l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Hugo Lloris c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm \u0110T Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho r\u1eb1ng Mbappe v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang phong c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, thay v\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Lloris ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Ph\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0110T Uruguay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-uruguay-noi-gi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-cavani-421-190472.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/tho-world-cup-tu-ket-bi-braxin.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-uruguay-noi-gi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-cavani-421-190472.html\">HLV Uruguay n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani?</span><br>\r\nHLV Oscar Tabarez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Edison Cavani, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 71 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG v\u1eabn b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-phap-21h-ngay-67-thu-manh-co-lai-cong-khung-421-190467.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Phap-(21h-ngay-67)-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-phap-21h-ngay-67-thu-manh-co-lai-cong-khung-421-190467.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 6/7): Th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng?</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu \u0111i v\u00e0o chi ti\u1ebft, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u00e1c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"958","checkdouble":"190478"},{"date":"10:30 06/07","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh: \"Colombia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng bi\u1ebft\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/cac-ngoi-sao-bong-da-nhung-nguoi-truyen-cam-hung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 v\u1ebb v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 John Stones ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T Colombia v\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o.\r\n</h2><h2>Colombia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng &ldquo;b\u1ea9n th\u1ec9u&rdquo; nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i sau khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Harry kane, Tam S\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang m\u1edbi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, Colombia li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Anh, khi nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 6 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, t\u1ea1o ra tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u gi\u00e0u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trung v\u1ec7 John Stones cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Colombia c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ea9n th\u1ec9u nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1. Khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 bao v\u00e2y tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea9y \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. Ngo\u00e0i ra c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Stones ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T Colombia v\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o\" title=\"Stones\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/cac-ngoi-sao-bong-da-nhung-nguoi-truyen-cam-hung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Stones ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T Colombia v\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phun ra t\u1eeb mi\u1ec7ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Colombia, m\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe \u0111\u1ebfn. Ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o \u00e2m m\u01b0u c\u1ee7a Colombia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh nhau v\u00e0 ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110T Anh c\u0169ng m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t trong nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">John Stones ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. \u0110\u00e3 qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Stones ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T Colombia, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1edbn v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vi-ly-do-nay-tuyen-anh-chap-nhan-mang-tieng-kich-si-421-190462.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/vi-ly-do-nay-tuyen-anh-chap-nhan-mang-tieng-kich-si.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vi-ly-do-nay-tuyen-anh-chap-nhan-mang-tieng-kich-si-421-190462.html\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do n\u00e0y, tuy\u1ec3n Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn mang ti\u1ebfng &ldquo;k\u1ecbch s\u0129&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nKieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng Tam s\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4n ngoan h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd tham d\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh-421-190417.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh-421-190417.html\">T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh</span><br>\r\nT\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1eb3ng ai quan t\u00e2m, \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"957","checkdouble":"190479"},{"date":"10:01 06/07","title":"Juventus l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/juventus-la-buoc-lui-su-nghiep-cua-ronaldo.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi, M10 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Lionel-Messi-muon-Barca-mua-Paul-Pogba-cua-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ed3 h\u1ee5t Griezmann ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi\u1ebfn Barca c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi, M10 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMessi hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta khi\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Barca b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Barca mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Pogba t\u1edbi Camp Nou, anh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Philippe Coutinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 cho Messi \u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Barca th\u00ec Real c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Pogba, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Luka Modric, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n Pogba, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 89.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1eeb Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/bat-chap-mau-thuan-voi-mourinho-pogba-se-o-lai-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 Paul Pogba cho Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua gi\u1eefa Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pogba c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi M.U, anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fred. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Pogba s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, nh\u1eb1m t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"956","checkdouble":"190480"},{"date":"09:37 06/07","title":"HLV Southgate: \"B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd cho \u0110T Anh\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/hlv-southgate-bay-gio-hoac-khong-bao-gio-cho-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7u tri\u1ec7u tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 47 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m-421-190321.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh sang trang l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</span> tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1edf n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi sau 12 n\u0103m to\u00e0n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eafng cay \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Tam S\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t t\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/hlv-southgate-bay-gio-hoac-khong-bao-gio-cho-dt-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00dd th\u1ee9c t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 quan tr\u1ecdng, HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh nh\u1eb1m hi\u1ec7u tri\u1ec7u tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: &ldquo;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn v\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o n\u1eefa trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, trong khi t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang ta. Sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0 d\u1eb7n, gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Southgate d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i x\u00e3 giao g\u00ec, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ef1ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu cho Anh khi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng thua trong hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 2002 v\u00e0 2006. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuu-hlv-anh-bat-ngo-ung-ho-thuy-dien-chien-thang-421-190396.html\">C\u1ef1u HLV Anh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-nguoi-hung-emil-forsberg-421-190326.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n-kh\u00f4ng-Ibra ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf World Cup: H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh phi th\u01b0\u1eddng vi\u1ebft b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"955","checkdouble":"190481"},{"date":"09:52 06/07","title":"B\u1ecb FIFA tu\u00fdt c\u00f2i v\u00ec l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n, Diego Maradona bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i xin l\u1ed7i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/bi-fifa-tuyt-coi-vi-long-ngon-diego-maradona-xin-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb FIFA c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o, Diego Maradona xin l\u1ed7i v\u00ec nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u thi\u1ebfu suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau khi \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia. </h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diego Maradona xin l\u1ed7i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng Diego Maradona khi\u1ebfn FIFA ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang m\u1ef1c sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8. Maradona t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 gh\u00e9t \u0110T Anh ra m\u1eb7t, ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Mark Geiger thi\u00ean v\u1ecb cho Tam S\u01b0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ecb FIFA tu\u00fdt c\u00f2i v\u00ec l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n, Diego Maradona xin l\u1ed7i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ecb FIFA tu\u00fdt c\u00f2i v\u00ec l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n, Diego Maradona xin l\u1ed7i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/bi-fifa-tuyt-coi-vi-long-ngon-diego-maradona-xin-loi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Diego Maradona xin l\u1ed7i sau khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang m\u1ef1c d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nFIFA sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn Maradona nh\u1eb1m nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf &quot;c\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng&quot; \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1i cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb \u0111ang nh\u1eadn.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb FIFA c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o, Maradona m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ph\u1ea3i g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i tr\u00ean Instagram c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: &quot;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00e0, xin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. Xin l\u1ed7i FIFA v\u00e0 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch. \u0110\u00f4i khi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maradona g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 World Cup 2018, Maradona g\u00e2y ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng b\u1ecb b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p ph\u00ec ph\u00e8o h\u00fat x\u00ec g\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Argentina vs Iceland, hay b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 gi\u01a1 ng\u00f3n tay th\u1ed1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Argentina vs Nigeria.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ra vi\u1ec7n, Maradona c\u0169ng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 trao gi\u1ea3i 8.000 b\u1ea3ng cho ai t\u00ecm ra tung t\u00edch k\u1ebb phao tin m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebft. Nh\u1eefng vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m, thi\u1ebfu suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a Maradona khi\u1ebfn FIFA \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o d\u00f9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Diego Maradona t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/fifa-ra-toi-hau-thu-cho-maradona-vi-thoi-long-ngon-421-190415.html\">FIFA ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho Maradona v\u00ec th\u00f3i l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/vua-bong-da-maradona-treo-thuong-8000-bang-truy-tim-ke-tung-tin-minh-chet-188-190165.html\">Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Maradona treo th\u01b0\u1edfng 8.000 b\u1ea3ng truy t\u00ecm k\u1ebb tung tin m\u00ecnh ch\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/maradona-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-bi-loai-421-190100.html\">Maradona: &ldquo;Argentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim ch\u1ebft ch\u00f3c&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/maradona-xuat-vien-toi-dang-cang-tran-suc-song-hon-bao-gio-het-421-189895.html\">Maradona xu\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7n: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u0103ng tr\u00e0n s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/maradona-phat-bieu-ve-iniesta-va-danh-loi-khen-421-190004.html\">Iniesta l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u00fd \u00f4ng, Ramos l\u00e0 k\u1ebb ph\u00e0m phu</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/maradona-bao-ve-messi-chi-trich-nhan-to-khac-cua-argentina-421-188795.html\">Maradona b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi, c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Argentina</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"954","checkdouble":"190482"},{"date":"10:26 06/07","title":"Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/messi-muon-barca-mua-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi, M10 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Lionel-Messi-muon-Barca-mua-Paul-Pogba-cua-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ed3 h\u1ee5t Griezmann ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi\u1ebfn Barca c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi, M10 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMessi hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta khi\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Barca b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Barca mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Pogba t\u1edbi Camp Nou, anh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Philippe Coutinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 cho Messi \u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Barca th\u00ec Real c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Pogba, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Luka Modric, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n Pogba, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 89.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1eeb Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/bat-chap-mau-thuan-voi-mourinho-pogba-se-o-lai-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 Paul Pogba cho Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua gi\u1eefa Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pogba c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi M.U, anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fred. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Pogba s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, nh\u1eb1m t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"953","checkdouble":"190483"},{"date":"11:11 06/07","title":"Jose Mourinho: \"Neymar kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u00e3 duy nh\u1ea5t l\u0103n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/jose-mourinho-noi-ve-thoi-an-va-tai-world-cp-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 cho r\u1eb1ng Neymar kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1i t\u00ean duy nh\u1ea5t s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u0103n ra s\u00e2n khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ebfn.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i k\u1ebb \u0103n v\u1ea1 duy nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tai ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t khi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u0103n ra \u0103n v\u1ea1 sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 14 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar an va tho thien\" title=\"Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/jose-mourinho-noi-ve-thoi-an-va-tai-world-cp-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jose Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 cho r\u1eb1ng Neymar kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1i t\u00ean duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m v\u1eady.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean theo Jose Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Neymar kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1i t\u00ean duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb l\u00ean \u00e1n: &quot;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadp trung qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o anh \u1ea5y nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u00ecnh Neymar l\u00e0m v\u1eady. \u0110\u1ed9i n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3 v\u1edd \u0111\u1eb7t \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn l\u00ean c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea5t \u0111i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1eeb. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia \u0111\u00e2u, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0103n v\u1ea1 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 VAR th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn t\u1ea1o ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0110T Anh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c, T\u00e2y Ban Nha hay Argentina s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, HLV Jose Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. \u1ede t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Tam S\u01b0 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, Mourinho nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: &quot;Trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec h\u1ecd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Nga ho\u1eb7c Croatia. T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 21h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Neymar t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lukaku-neymar-khong-phai-mot-dien-vien-421-190471.html\">Lukaku: Neymar kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ro-beo-neymar-co-the-gianh-qua-bong-vang-2018-421-190440.html\">R\u00f4 b\u00e9o: Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thong-ke-day-an-tuong-tai-world-cup-2018-ve-neymar-an-va-465-190423.html\">Neymar d\u00e0nh 1/6 th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/real-duoc-khuyen-no-2-bom-tan-neymar-va-mbappe-184-190413.html\">Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u1ed5 2 bom t\u1ea5n Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dan-anh-bao-ve-thoi-an-va-cua-neymar-421-190406.html\">Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/willian-ca-ngoi-neymar-giua-nhung-chi-trich-421-190404.html\">Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"952","checkdouble":"190489"},{"date":"11:00 06/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/24/thuc-hu-vu-klopp-muon-liverpool-mua-xherdan-shaqiri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ph\u00eda Stoke City x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Xherdan Shaqiri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir, Lyon th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi The Kop v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. G\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 v\u1ee5 ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/thuc-hu-vu-klopp-muon-liverpool-mua-xherdan-shaqiri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Shaqiri\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Klopp quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Stoke City. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Stoke, anh ghi t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 7 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKlopp tin r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Stoke ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Xherdan Shaqiri l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. C\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Anfield.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Xherdan Shaqiri s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Liverpool, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Klopp \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Stoke x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Liverrpool ch\u01b0a h\u1ecfi mua Xherdan Shaqiri</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ph\u00eda Stoke City x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xherdan Shaqiri\" title=\"Xherdan Shaqiri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/6/Chelsea-va-Man-City-ap-dao-DHTB-vong-11-Premier-League-hinh-anh-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Stoke x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua Xherdan Shaqiri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb s\u00e2n Bet365 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Stoke c\u00f2n \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch\u00a0gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-12-trieu-bang-mua-chu-lun-de-thuong-172-190422.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Shaqiri</span>, theo \u0111\u00f3 Mourinho \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Shaqiri v\u00e0 Stoke c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3, b\u1edfi v\u1eady s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Shaqiri. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"951","checkdouble":"190490"},{"date":"11:14 06/07","title":"Barca g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 2 mua sao Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/21/barca-gui-loi-de-nghi-thu-2-mua-sao-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mua Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, sau khi h\u1ee5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Antoine Griezmann t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid, Blaugrana chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mua Willian v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mua Willian v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Barca-mua-Willian-voi-so-tien-cuc-khung-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Willian b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhilippe Coutinho \u0111ang th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c Barca mua Willian, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Willian \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean mua Willian, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb\u00a0c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-khong-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-189958.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Barca</span>, h\u1ecd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Willian r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Willian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Barca n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 2 t\u1edbi Chelsea. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Barca mua Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian la cai ten choi noi bat trong hiep mot tran Chelsea vs West Ham.\" title=\"Willian l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Chelsea vs West Ham.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/willian.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Willian l\u00ean 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed The Blues c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. Theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Martial c\u1ee7a M.U nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Brazil, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWillian v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, ngo\u00e0i Barca th\u00ec MU c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"950","checkdouble":"190491"},{"date":"11:28 06/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, sao Brazil khi\u1ebfn Kompany ph\u1ea3i x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/6/truoc-dai-chien-sao-brazil-khien-kompany-phai-xau-ho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u, trung v\u1ec7 Brazil Miranda chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3.\r\n</h2><h2>B\u1ec9 \u0111ang run s\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Selecao<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, trung v\u1ec7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/kompany-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-bi-vs-brazil-421-190392.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kompany n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 v\u00ec Brazil</span>, v\u00e0 anh tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd - Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo trung v\u1ec7 Miranda c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil, Kompany ch\u1ec9 &ldquo;n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n, ch\u1ee9 B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t s\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Selecao. Trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khi\u00eau kh\u00edch. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Kompany ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 che gi\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, v\u00e0 che gi\u1ea5u n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Miranda chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn\" title=\"Miranda n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/truoc-dai-chien-sao-brazil-khien-kompany-phai-xau-ho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Miranda chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Brazil, v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, Kompany ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n ni\u1ec1m tin cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Miranda c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y: &ldquo;\u0110T B\u1ec9 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed7i Lukaku. \u0110\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, B\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u1ecd c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 nguy hi\u1ec3m trong nh\u1eefng pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7&rdquo; &ndash; Miranda chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang mong ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u1eefa Brazil vs B\u1ec9. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay ho\u1eb7c Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bi-danh-gia-cuc-cao-brazil-421-190476.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/hlv-bi-danh-gia-cuc-cao-brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bi-danh-gia-cuc-cao-brazil-421-190476.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao Brazil</span><br>\r\nRoberto Martinez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9, c\u1ef1u HLV Everton \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Selecao.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-bi-01h00-ngay-77-bua-tiec-tan-cong-421-190475.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/Roberto-Martinez-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Brazil-vs-Bi-hinh-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-bi-01h00-ngay-77-bua-tiec-tan-cong-421-190475.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs B\u1ec9 (01h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7): B\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</span><br>\r\n2 trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs B\u1ec9 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tru-cot-danilo-chan-thuong-nghi-het-world-cup-421-190464.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/tru-cot-danilo-chan-thuong-nghi-het-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tru-cot-danilo-chan-thuong-nghi-het-world-cup-421-190464.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Brazil ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft World Cup</span><br>\r\nDanilo ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0110T Brazil ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ecd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"949","checkdouble":"190492"},{"date":"07:19 06/07","title":"Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Brazil ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/tru-cot-danilo-chan-thuong-nghi-het-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu \u0111i v\u00e0o chi ti\u1ebft, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. T\u1edbi gi\u1edd ph\u00fat n\u00e0y, Les Bleus \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y qua tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Didier Deschamps d\u1eabn d\u1eaft ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. B\u1ed9 ba Griezmann, Giroud v\u00e0 Mbappe ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t \u0103n \u00fd v\u00e0 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Uruguay, \u0111\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2-1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 67) t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 67) t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Phap-(21h-ngay-67)-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p 21h ng\u00e0y 6/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p, kh\u00f4ng ai d\u00e1m xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. T\u00ednh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Diego Godin c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Sau 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng Uruguay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a g\u1eb7p thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 m\u00ecnh Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn La Celeste g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ai C\u1eadp, Saudi Arabia r\u1ed3i Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani ghi ban cho Uruguay truoc Nga\" title=\"Cavani ghi ban cho Uruguay truoc Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/HLV-Tabarez-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Uruguay-3-0-Nga-day-nuoi-tiec-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Uruguay ch\u01b0a g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i c\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. Tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Fekir, Dembele, Thauvin hay Lemar \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u00e0i v\u00e0 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Kante c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t \u1edf ph\u00eda sau, Ph\u00e1p c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pogba m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 15 l\u00e1 ph\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1p nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1. Ch\u00ednh Kante \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n h\u1ed3i sinh Pogba sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a nh\u01b0 \u00fd t\u1ea1i Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o gu\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 n\u1eefa l\u00e0 Uruguay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 (sau Peru v\u00e0 Argentina).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe-421-190444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe-421-190444.html\">Ph\u00e1p th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup: C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng mang t\u00ean Pogbappe</span><br>\r\n<span>Kazan, 30 th\u00e1ng S\u00e1u 2018, Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chia tay World Cup, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e3i m\u00e3i, \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i cho...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nUruguay thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Uruguay s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi mang t\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Uruguay. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb b\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1ee3c khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Tabarez d\u1eabn d\u1eaft thi\u1ebfu \u0111i Cavani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani chan thuong nghi tran vs Phap\" title=\"Cavani chan thuong nghi tran vs Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Cavani-chan-thuong-nghi-tran-vs-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi\u1ebfn Cavani kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Uruguay b\u1edfi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf PSG \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Suarez \u1edf th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Uruguay. Hu\u1ed1ng chi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018 t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi sau khi c\u00e0y \u1ea3i c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a c\u00f9ng Barcelona. Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a La Celeste ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"griezmann va Suarez\" title=\"griezmann va Suarez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/griezmann-va-Suarez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u1ec9 Suarez kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng so \u0111\u1ecd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Uruguay. Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u HLV Tabarez mong mu\u1ed1n. Song c\u0169ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Cavani.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, Tabarez s\u1ebd c\u00f3 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t gi\u00e0, m\u1ed9t tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 Cristhian Stuani v\u00e0 Maxi Gomez. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Stuani (31 tu\u1ed5i) ch\u1ec9 ghi 5 b\u00e0n sau 40 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Uruguay. C\u00f2n Gomez (21 tu\u1ed5i) m\u1edbi c\u00f3 6 tr\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang-469-190410.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang-469-190410.html\">Trung v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Trung v\u1ec7 Adil Rami \u0111\u00e3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cavani d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 8 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, ch\u1ec9 Nga (21) l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Uruguay (25). Khi v\u1eafng &ldquo;tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o&rdquo; Cavani, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eddi c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a La Celeste c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod 21h t\u1ed1i nay (6/7): Uruguay co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u1eb1m c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc l\u00f3e s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Les Bleus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nUruguay (4-3-2-1):</strong> 1.Muslera - 22.C\u00e1ceres, 2.Gim\u00e9nez, 3.God\u00edn, 17.Laxalt - 8.N\u00e1ndez, 14.Torreira, 15.Vecino - 6.Bentancur, 10.Arrascaeta - 9.Su\u00e1rez<br>\r\n<strong>Ph\u00e1p (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Lloris - 2.Pavard, 4.Varane, 5.Umtiti, 21.Hern\u00e1ndez - 13.Kant\u00e9, 6.Pogba - 10.Mbapp\u00e9, 7.Griezmann, 18.Fekir - 9.Giroud<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: </strong>Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Uruguay vs Phap\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Uruguay-vs-Phap-(4-3-2-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/antoine-griezmann-phu-phang-voi-diego-godin-421-190167.html\">Antoine Griezmann ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Diego Godin</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-uruguay-xac-nhan-kha-nang-ra-san-cua-cavani-o-tran-gap-dt-phap-421-190362.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 Uruguay c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/da-bai-bo-dao-nha-hlv-uruguay-no-tung-bung-469-190071.html\">\u0110\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, HLV Uruguay n\u1ed5 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/matuidi-khang-dinh-mbappe-se-toa-sang-hon-nua-469-190408.html\">Matuidi tin Mbappe s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn h\u1ea1 Uruguay \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/torreira-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-uruguay-vs-phap-421-190425.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"948","checkdouble":"190464"},{"date":"07:40 06/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/nguoi-dai-dien-vo-tinh-lam-lo-tuong-lai-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jorge Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo. \u201cSi\u00eau c\u00f2\u201d n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng n\u00e0y v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin CR7 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus chi \u0111\u1eadm cho Ronaldo</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (100 tri\u1ec7u Euro) t\u1edbi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 44 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n9 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i Real, Ronaldo c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu chinh ph\u1ee5c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 4 Champions League v\u00e0 2 La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Mendes-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-tai-Real-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f3 tin Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n nh\u1edb ngay sau khi Real \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd, nghe \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Man United \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ m\u00f9a. Ch\u00ednh c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Luciano Moggi \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mendes v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJorge Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo trong l\u00fac d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn s\u1ee5c s\u00f4i. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y g\u1ee3i \u00fd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Qua \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec vi\u1ec7c Mendes x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Juventus trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorge Mendes bi tinh nghi tron thue.\" title=\"Jorge Mendes b\u1ecb t\u00ecnh nghi tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/13/sau-cris-ronaldo-sieu-co-jorge-mendes-bi-dieu-tra-tron-thue.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mendes ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea9n \u00fd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd m\u00e3i m\u00e3i bi\u1ebft \u01a1n CLB, ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean y t\u1ebf, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c Madridistas tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi&rdquo;, Mendes n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd Record. &ldquo;M\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u1edbi v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Real t\u1eeb Man United n\u0103m 2009, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n sau 438 tr\u1eadn cho h\u1ecd tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus-180-190379.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 95% Ronaldo c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-24-de-che-siro-chua-the-sup-do-421-190218.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 24: \u0110\u1ebf ch\u1ebf &ldquo;Si-R\u00f4&rdquo; ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/an-tuong-world-cup/cristiano-ronaldo-cau-thu-co-tam-va-tai-471-190213.html\">B\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup: Cristiano Ronaldo - C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-va-messi-dat-tay-nhau-ve-nuoc-doan-ket-cuoc-hanh-trinh-421-190180.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc: \u0110o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"947","checkdouble":"190465"},{"date":"07:56 06/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 6/7: Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-67-ronaldo-gan-nhu-la-nguoi-cua-juve.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 6/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Messi mu\u1ed1n Pogba t\u1edbi Barcelona.</strong> Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barcelona k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba t\u1eeb Manchester United. Sau khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 Antoine Griezmann m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u00fa \u00fd sang m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c. Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Paulinho khu trung tuy\u1ebfn Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve. </strong>Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Goal, Cristiano Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus. CR7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A v\u1ec1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ m\u00f9a. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 khi\u1ebfn cho ph\u00eda Real Madrid b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi h\u1ecd mong ch\u1edd Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 67 Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 67 Ronaldo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juve h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Mendes-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-Ronaldo-tai-Real-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f3 tin Ronaldo chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Argentina mu\u1ed1n thay Sampaoli. </strong>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Mario Kempes mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV Argentina n\u1ebfu&nbsp; Jorge Sampaoli b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i. Sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Sampaoli lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i d\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Shaqiri. </strong>Manchester United s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri t\u1eeb Stoke City. Theo t\u1edd The Sun, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, ch\u00ednh c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Napoli m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho Jorginho t\u1edbi Man City. </strong>Napoli m\u1edbi c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Fabian Ruiz t\u1eeb Real Betis. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Napoli coi nh\u01b0 m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho t\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Jorginho\" title=\"tien ve Jorginho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/26/man-city-sap-co-jorginho-cua-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Jorginho r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda sang Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nBarca g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi cho Willian.</strong> Barcelona \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Sau khi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1edf h\u1eefu tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil th\u00f4ng qua con s\u1ed1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Tottenham v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Liverpol trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Grealish. </strong>Theo t\u1edd Mirror, Tottenham s\u1eafp gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool khi ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi anh.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nSouthgate v\u1eabn c\u1ea7m l\u00e1i Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2022.</strong> Ngay t\u1eeb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n HLV Gareth Southgate. Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Telegraph, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a Tam s\u01b0 t\u1edbi VCK Euro 2020, Southgate s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho t\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 n\u0103m 2022.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"946","checkdouble":"190466"},{"date":"08:05 06/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 6/7): Th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Phap-(21h-ngay-67)-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu \u0111i v\u00e0o chi ti\u1ebft, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. T\u1edbi gi\u1edd ph\u00fat n\u00e0y, Les Bleus \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y qua tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Didier Deschamps d\u1eabn d\u1eaft ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. B\u1ed9 ba Griezmann, Giroud v\u00e0 Mbappe ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t \u0103n \u00fd v\u00e0 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Uruguay, \u0111\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2-1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 67) t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 67) t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Phap-(21h-ngay-67)-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p 21h ng\u00e0y 6/7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p, kh\u00f4ng ai d\u00e1m xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. T\u00ednh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Diego Godin c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Sau 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng Uruguay v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a g\u1eb7p thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 m\u00ecnh Cristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn La Celeste g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ai C\u1eadp, Saudi Arabia r\u1ed3i Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani ghi ban cho Uruguay truoc Nga\" title=\"Cavani ghi ban cho Uruguay truoc Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/HLV-Tabarez-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Uruguay-3-0-Nga-day-nuoi-tiec-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Uruguay ch\u01b0a g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u0169i c\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. Tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Fekir, Dembele, Thauvin hay Lemar \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u00e0i v\u00e0 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Kante c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t \u1edf ph\u00eda sau, Ph\u00e1p c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pogba m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 15 l\u00e1 ph\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1p nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1. Ch\u00ednh Kante \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n h\u1ed3i sinh Pogba sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a nh\u01b0 \u00fd t\u1ea1i Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o gu\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 n\u1eefa l\u00e0 Uruguay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 (sau Peru v\u00e0 Argentina).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe-421-190444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-thang-tien-tu-ket-world-cup-cong-thuc-chien-thang-mang-ten-pogbappe-421-190444.html\">Ph\u00e1p th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup: C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng mang t\u00ean Pogbappe</span><br>\r\n<span>Kazan, 30 th\u00e1ng S\u00e1u 2018, Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chia tay World Cup, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e3i m\u00e3i, \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i cho...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nUruguay thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, Uruguay s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u00ean nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Edinson Cavani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi mang t\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Uruguay. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb b\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1ee3c khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Tabarez d\u1eabn d\u1eaft thi\u1ebfu \u0111i Cavani.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani chan thuong nghi tran vs Phap\" title=\"Cavani chan thuong nghi tran vs Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Cavani-chan-thuong-nghi-tran-vs-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi\u1ebfn Cavani kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Uruguay b\u1edfi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf PSG \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Suarez \u1edf th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Uruguay. Hu\u1ed1ng chi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2018 t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi sau khi c\u00e0y \u1ea3i c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a c\u00f9ng Barcelona. Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a La Celeste ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"griezmann va Suarez\" title=\"griezmann va Suarez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/griezmann-va-Suarez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u1ec9 Suarez kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng so \u0111\u1ecd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Uruguay. Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u HLV Tabarez mong mu\u1ed1n. Song c\u0169ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Cavani.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u00ean, Tabarez s\u1ebd c\u00f3 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t gi\u00e0, m\u1ed9t tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 Cristhian Stuani v\u00e0 Maxi Gomez. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Stuani (31 tu\u1ed5i) ch\u1ec9 ghi 5 b\u00e0n sau 40 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Uruguay. C\u00f2n Gomez (21 tu\u1ed5i) m\u1edbi c\u00f3 6 tr\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang-469-190410.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang-469-190410.html\">Trung v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Trung v\u1ec7 Adil Rami \u0111\u00e3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cavani d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 8 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, ch\u1ec9 Nga (21) l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u00edt c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Uruguay (25). Khi v\u1eafng &ldquo;tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o&rdquo; Cavani, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eddi c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a La Celeste c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod 21h t\u1ed1i nay (6/7): Uruguay co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u1eb1m c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc l\u00f3e s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Les Bleus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nUruguay (4-3-2-1):</strong> 1.Muslera - 22.C\u00e1ceres, 2.Gim\u00e9nez, 3.God\u00edn, 17.Laxalt - 8.N\u00e1ndez, 14.Torreira, 15.Vecino - 6.Bentancur, 10.Arrascaeta - 9.Su\u00e1rez<br>\r\n<strong>Ph\u00e1p (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Lloris - 2.Pavard, 4.Varane, 5.Umtiti, 21.Hern\u00e1ndez - 13.Kant\u00e9, 6.Pogba - 10.Mbapp\u00e9, 7.Griezmann, 18.Fekir - 9.Giroud<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: </strong>Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Uruguay vs Phap\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Uruguay-vs-Phap-(4-3-2-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/antoine-griezmann-phu-phang-voi-diego-godin-421-190167.html\">Antoine Griezmann ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Diego Godin</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-uruguay-xac-nhan-kha-nang-ra-san-cua-cavani-o-tran-gap-dt-phap-421-190362.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 Uruguay c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/da-bai-bo-dao-nha-hlv-uruguay-no-tung-bung-469-190071.html\">\u0110\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, HLV Uruguay n\u1ed5 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/matuidi-khang-dinh-mbappe-se-toa-sang-hon-nua-469-190408.html\">Matuidi tin Mbappe s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn h\u1ea1 Uruguay \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/torreira-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-uruguay-vs-phap-421-190425.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"945","checkdouble":"190467"},{"date":"08:42 06/07","title":"R\u1eddi Juventus sang Real Madrid, Ronaldo mang l\u1ed9c cho Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/roi-juventus-sang-real-madrid-ronaldo-mang-loc-cho-man-utd.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Manchester United v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Sporting Lisbon s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i hoa h\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n 2,5% trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus mua Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y: <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, CR7 s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Bernabeu, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 kh\u00f3 ai ng\u1edd t\u1edbi cho si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro khi Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro khi Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/roi-juventus-sang-real-madrid-ronaldo-mang-loc-cho-man-utd.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro khi Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u00e0 Juventus, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p l\u1eafm ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain hay tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a Manchester United. \u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester sau bao \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ee9a con c\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb c\u00e1c C\u0110V, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 vui v\u1ebb v\u00ec nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u201ctr\u00ean tr\u1eddi r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, Man Utd s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i hoa h\u1ed3ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n 2,5% trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus mua Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 2,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro hay 2,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea3 CLB kh\u1edfi nghi\u1ec7p Sporting Lisbon c\u1ee7a CR7 c\u0169ng h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 1,9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec trong b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2009, Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Real Madrid b\u00e1n Ronaldo trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, nh\u01b0ng lu\u1eadt l\u1ec7 chung v\u1eabn cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Sporting Lisbon \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng khi chia tay nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb do ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng ho\u00e0ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus</span> v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB gi\u00e0u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-dai-dien-vo-tinh-lam-lo-tuong-lai-ronaldo-421-190465.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/juventus-coi-nhu-trung-xo-so-neu-chieu-mo-duoc-ronaldo-184-190455.html\">Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo, Serie A coi nh\u01b0 tr\u00fang s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eafc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"944","checkdouble":"190468"}]}